item.dc:creator: @Daginith Daginith
item.description:
@Daginith wrote:

RiiPiiNFtW:

Looks like an extra bracket.

Nah, it says ‘illegal start’ that means there is no closing bracket.

Your missing a bracket some place. Open up the code with Notepad++ or something similar, it helps alot, so you can view where the brackets open and close.
